::DarkMouse::

She heard her name being called and she looked at Quickstrike 
pointing at her.  She stood up and put Akura on her shoulder and 
walked over to Quickstrike.
"I found this one here," points ti the rat on her shoulder," knawing 
on a few wires in my console.  I'm keeping him. Don't worry, I'll 
build him a cage shortly so he won't get into anymore trouble."
